ies wailing over them.\u201d Ibn al-Mubarak said, \u201cI hope he would be spared from that if he prohibited them while he was alive.\u201d Source: Sunan al-Tirmidhi\u0304 1002 Grade: Sahih\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":14653,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/06\/08\/visit-graves-remember-akhirah\/","url_meta":{"origin":21189,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Graves: Visit graveyards to remember the Hereafter","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"June 8, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Mas\u2019ud reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cI had prohibited you from visiting graves, but you may visit them now. Verily, they will weaken your attachment to the world and remind you of the Hereafter.\" Source: Sunan Ibn Ma\u0304jah 1571 Grade: Sahih (authentic)\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":35519,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2021\/04\/03\/prophet-prays-servant\/","url_meta":{"origin":21189,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Funerals: The Prophet prays for a humble mosque servant","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"April 3, 2021","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: A black woman, or a young man, used to maintain the mosque and one day the Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, missed her and asked about her. They said, \u201cShe has died.\u201d The Prophet said, \u201cYou would not announce it to me?\u201d It\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":5503,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/08\/24\/qabr-first-stage-akhirah\/","url_meta":{"origin":21189,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Qabr: Grave is first stage of the Hereafter","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"August 24, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Uthman reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cVerily, the grave is the first stage of the Hereafter. If one is saved from it, whatever comes after will be easier for him. If one is not saved from it, whatever comes after will be harder for him.\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]}],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/21189","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/3712"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=21189"}],"version-history":[{"count":0,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/21189\/revisions"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dail